Corey Benjamin sraral hya'ga sisyow na NBA, wal malaxmisoq qaniy la. kawas te 1978, byacing te 2 ro 24 ryax qo hintgan nya, kinholan nya ga California, hiya ga mnanak na ppzoy mari waya, ro sqoliq ka ppkal mari waya. 198 konbon kinwagiq nya, 91 konkin kin'sow nya, hiya ga qotox nqo spzyang blaq na ppzoy mari NBA. kawas 1998 mnwayaw ppzoy mari ga, mzyop sqo te qotox lahoy ro te magal sqoliq, galon nqo Chicago Bolls. 2002-2003 kawas Corey Benjamin maki Bolls cyogal pspong. qnxan nya Benjamin sqoliq na Oregon Beavers. hiya ga ro Sonny sangka' qotox hlahoy na mzyo mari. cinkholan sa knita' sa brbiro' Lists of National Basketball Association players
